	(create_memmaps_tree): Renamed COL_* to MMAP_COL* to avoid conflict.
	Use MMAP_COL_* wherever possible.
	(sort_guint64): Don't truncate guint64 to gint anymore.
	
	* src/proctable.c: Removed useless #includes.

